#SKEENEE

Cryptoart OG 2019 | Skeleton Re-Animator | Middle Finger Painter | Metaverse Pioneer | Art Pyromaniac  

"Madrid based Belgian artist obsessed with skulls and anatomy in general. Creation is my passion. Art is a research. Instead of merely copying reality, my focus is to understand what lies behind it, to see past the details and find the essence of things. Every curve has a life, a reason to be, a beginning and an end, a personality."
